  "detailed_description": "GX  Sudoku is just a basic classic Sudoku game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPress New to generate a new puzzle<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPress Solve to solve the puzzle<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPress the ESC key to quit the game<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou click on the boxes and type number in.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe boxes light up green when you complete the puzzle <br />\r\n<br />\r\nEndless hours of sudoku fun<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGenerates a new puzzle each time.",
